org.apache.ignite.lang

Class IgniteProductVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.lang.IgniteProductVersion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable, Comparable<IgniteProductVersion>

    public class IgniteProductVersion
extends Object
implements Comparable<IgniteProductVersion>, Externalizable
    Represents node version.

    Node version can be acquired via ClusterNode.version() method.

    Two versions are compared in the following order: major number, minor number, maintenance number, revision timestamp.

    See Also:
